Localization.Name: Greycat Industrial
Localization.Description: A trusted manufacturer of industrial tools since 2337, the company’s extensive line of industrial equipment and armor make it one of the most respected brand names around. Greycat has remained a UEE staple for centuries thanks to their streamlined-yet-inventive designs, exacting safety standards, and a diverse product line.

Localization.Name: Cambio SRT
Localization.Description:
Manufacturer: Greycat Industrial
Item Type: Utility
Class: Gadget

Canister Size: Large
Rate of Fire: N / A (Beam)
Effective Range: 5 m

Strip salvage and make repairs with the Cambio, a dual purpose salvage and repair tool (SRT) designed to collect and convert alloys and polymers found in scrap into recycled material composite that can either be sold or used to make quick repairs. The Cambio SRT features rapid stripping speeds and an impressive battery life, making it an essential gadget for mechanics and spacefarers.
